title: Kylie Jenner to have ‘booze’ filled 18th b’day bash in Canada
text:
Other Articles Hulk Hogan mourns wrestler pal Roddy Piper's death Daniel Radcliffe to play FBI agent in 'Imperium' We still call Caitlyn Jenner 'Bruce': Khloe Kardashian Kylie Jenner is heading to Canada for her 18th birthday on August 10 to get legally wasted.
The 17-year-old Kylie Jenner is throwing a bash at Beachclub Montreal, which is equivalent to Ibiza, a mini party island with a beach, pool, A-list DJs and of course alcohol, TMZ.com reported.
On top of that, Kylie Jenner’s actually getting paid to be there, somewhere between 100,000- 200,000 dollars only for showing up.
The club’s owner, Olivier Primeau, will be going all out to give Kylie Jenner the best experience with a chopper bringing her in, landing on a luxury boat that will dock next to a table stocked with booze, and a 3,000 dollars cake.
First Published on July 31, 2015 3:40 pm
